cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling in statistical machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel approach to language modeling. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves natural language processing and modeling. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the quality of translation. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves rendering and compositing phrases.
